<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Resume 2</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />

    <style>

    :root {
  --bg-dark: #0a0a0a;             /* Overall background */
  --text-light: #ffffff;         /* Main white text */
  --accent-blue: #00d2ff;        /* Neon blue accent (lines, highlights) */
  --text-muted: #bbbbbb;         /* Sub text or secondary info */
  --card-bg: #121212;            /* Section box background */
  --skill-bg: #1e1e1e;           /* Skill icon background */
  --skill-border: #00bfff;       /* Skill icon border */
}


    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      color: var(--text-light);
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    }

    main{
        height: 100vh;
        width: 100%;
        padding-top: 3%;
        background-color: #eff6e0;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .resume{
        height:90%;
        width: 35%;
        background-color: var(--bg-dark);
        padding: 2%;
    }

    .nav{
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        border-bottom: 3px solid var(--skill-border);
        padding-bottom:3%;
    }

    .nav h2{
        font-weight: 700;
        font-size: 2.3rem;
    }
    .nav h4{
        font-weight: 200;
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom:0.5rem;
        color: var(--accent-blue);
    }
    .img{
        height: 130px;
        width: 130px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        border: 2px solid var(--skill-border);
    }

    .nav p{
        font-size: 1rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
    }

    .nav i{
        color: var(--accent-blue);
    }

    section{
        margin-top: 5%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
    }

    .summary{
        width: 50%;
        height: 150px;
        background-color:var(--skill-bg);
        border-right: 2px solid var(--skill-border);
    }

     .skill{
        width: 50%;
        height: 150px;
        background-color:var(--skill-bg);
        border-left: 2px solid var(--skill-border);
        padding-left: 1rem;
    }

    .skill h3,p{
        /* margin-left: 1rem; */
    }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <main>
        <div class="resume">
           <div class="nav">
            <div class="img"></div>
            <div class="text">
                <h2>Nishav Chaudhary</h2>
                <h4>Devloper</h4>
                <p><i class="fa-solid fa-envelope"></i>&nbsp; @email.com &nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp; <i class="fa-solid fa-phone"></i>&nbsp;9148119744 <br><i class="fa-solid fa-location-dot"></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Bangalore</p>
            </div>
           </div>

           <section>
            <div class="summary">
                <h3>Summary</h3>
                <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. A suscipit ex quos recusandae dolorem veritatis et cupiditate sed possimus illo. Obcaecati repudiandae, sequi pariatur quasi eos sint quam ad corporis.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="skill">
                <h3>Skill</h3>
                <p>skills</p>
            </div>
           </section>
        </div>

        <button id="down">Download</button>
    </main>
</body>
</html>